{"tid":559063,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[關愛座] 6旬翁拿刀怒捅未讓座年輕人","createTime":"2018-02-13T00:33:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-13T03:58:41.000Z","uid":35468,"like":19,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"5a6d86a01258d60300cd2ba47a20dc2b833c5340","tid":559063,"uid":35468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T00:33:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2340571\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2340571&d=naZqUvrmHkgCcgPIqat5xhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=c9d445d5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2340571&h=d6ed96ef\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2340571</a><br />\n<br />\n日本一位老人最近因為不滿年輕人沒讓座，於是拿出刀械攻擊對方，遭警方逮捕。<br />\n<br />\n綜合日媒報導，日本大阪7日發生一起攻擊事件，一位62歲老人在大阪搭乘地鐵時，看到一位34歲男子一直坐在優先座上沒讓座，於是心生不滿。老人隨後拿出隨身攜帶的水果刀刺進未讓座男子的腹部，造成該男子重傷，事後老人遭日本警方以殺人未遂罪嫌逮捕。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，日本在2015年也曾發生類似情形，當時一位71歲老人不滿另一位50歲男子在優先座附近滑平板，於是拿出菜刀意圖攻擊對方，最後遭逮捕。"},{"pid":"8cfe2557326f3595a394fce1db0aa7e8c3851568","tid":559063,"uid":109136,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T00:40:06.000Z","msg":"世界各地都有呢d仆街廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2686679386ea4c916b673247f8eb0571a0874340","tid":559063,"uid":3454,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T00:41:34.000Z","msg":"老人隨後拿出隨身攜帶的水果刀<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n榴槤乜乜乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"188d5db30209e9bf54dcdaa129e418651c23415c","tid":559063,"uid":38671,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T00:41:48.000Z","msg":"Baby boomers係世界毒瘤"},{"pid":"9349b11fd8d9ac203c63ff0b1e0cd409d29538a4","tid":559063,"uid":35644,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T00:43:54.000Z","msg":"一位7